        <span class="cs-meta-label">Services</span>
        <span class="cs-meta-value">Web Design, Local SEO</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-meta-item">
        <span class="cs-meta-label">Timeline</span>
        <span class="cs-meta-value">6 Weeks</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-meta-item">
        <span class="cs-meta-label">Year</span>
        <span class="cs-meta-value">2025</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  THE CHALLENGE (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>A Clinic Losing Patients to Competitors with Better Websites</h2>
        <p>
          LifeCare Clinic had been operating in Navrangpura for over 12 years with a strong offline reputation. Patients who walked in through referrals were consistently satisfied. But the online story was different.
        </p>
        <p>
          Their website was built in 2018, loaded in 8 seconds on mobile, and had no appointment booking system. When patients searched "clinic near Navrangpura" or "doctor in Ahmedabad," LifeCare did not appear in the local pack. Competitors with newer websites were capturing those searches daily.
        </p>
        <p>
          The clinic's management noticed a clear pattern: new patient inquiries were slowing down even as footfall in the area was increasing. Existing patients referred others, but those referrals would Google the clinic, land on the slow site, and sometimes call a competitor instead because the competitor's site had clear information and an easy contact form.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-challenge-list">
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>8-second load time on mobile</strong>
              <p>Uncompressed images, no caching, render-blocking scripts</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Not appearing in local search</strong>
              <p>Incomplete Google Business Profile, zero local schema markup</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No appointment booking system</strong>
              <p>Patients had to call during working hours — friction that lost leads</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No doctor profiles or service pages</strong>
              <p>Patients could not find the right specialist for their condition</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  OUR APPROACH (dark bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label light">Our Approach</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>Discovery First. Design Second. Results Third.</h2>
        <p>
          Before touching a single design file, we spent two sessions with the clinic's management team understanding their patient demographics, the most common search queries they were missing, and which competitor sites were winning the local search rankings. This informed every decision that followed.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-process-steps">
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">01</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Discovery and Competitor Audit</h4>
              <p>Audited 6 competing clinics in Ahmedabad. Identified keyword gaps, reviewed their GBP completeness, and mapped the content they had that LifeCare was missing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">02</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Information Architecture</h4>
              <p>Restructured the site around patient intent: specialities, individual doctors, conditions treated, and a clear path to booking. Every page designed to answer one specific patient question.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">03</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Mobile-First Design</h4>
              <p>Designed for Android phones first, then scaled up. Most clinic searches in Ahmedabad happen on mobile while patients are commuting or in waiting rooms. The new site loads in under 2 seconds on a 4G connection.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">04</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Local SEO Foundation</h4>
              <p>Added LocalBusiness schema, MedicalOrganization schema, optimised all meta titles with Ahmedabad neighbourhoods, and rebuilt the Google Business Profile with complete service listings and 20+ photos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">05</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Appointment System Integration</h4>
              <p>Integrated a simple online appointment form available 24/7. Patients can select their preferred doctor, department, and date. The clinic receives instant email and WhatsApp notifications.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  WHAT WE BUILT (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label">Deliverables</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>Everything Delivered, Nothing Left Half Done</h2>
        <p>
          The project scope was agreed in writing before a single pixel was designed. Here is exactly what was delivered within the 6-week timeline.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-deliverables-grid">
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎨</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Custom Website Design</h4>
              <p>18 pages with custom design. No templates. Built for healthcare trust signals: clean layout, professional photography placeholders, accessibility-compliant contrast.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">👨‍⚕️</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Doctor Profiles (8 doctors)</h4>
              <p>Dedicated profile pages for every doctor with specialisation, qualifications, experience, and a direct appointment link.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📋</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Service and Department Pages</h4>
              <p>12 condition-specific pages covering cardiology, orthopaedics, paediatrics, and more. Each optimised for local Ahmedabad keywords.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📅</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Online Appointment System</h4>
              <p>24/7 appointment form with doctor selection, department filter, preferred date, and instant notification to the clinic via email and WhatsApp.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Local SEO Setup</h4>
              <p>Full schema markup (LocalBusiness, MedicalOrganization, FAQPage), Google Business Profile rebuild, 15 location-specific meta tags, and Google Maps integration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Performance Optimisation</h4>
              <p>WebP images throughout, lazy loading, server caching, and minified CSS and JS. Final PageSpeed score: 96 on mobile, 99 on desktop.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  RESULTS (dark bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label light">The Results</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:white;">Numbers That Speak for Themselves</h2>
